0:00:00.000,0:00:08.260
Hano hari umugabo hano bamurega ko yishe umugabo.

0:00:08.260,0:00:10.260
Ndashaka ko aza hano.

0:00:10.260,0:00:16.380
Ntabwo ari umwe gusa, ndabona 'ababa bawe babiri bapfuye muri ubwo buryo.

0:00:16.380,0:00:18.240
Ngwino.

0:00:18.240,0:00:23.000
Ikintu cyarabaye. Ni nk'aho mwari mu nzu.

0:00:23.000,0:00:26.120
Ese yaba ari inzu nshya? Mwaba mwari muri gutaha iyo nzu?

0:00:26.120,0:00:29.820
Ni iki bakoraga muri iyo nzu nshyashya?

0:00:29.820,0:00:35.040
Nuko ako kanya ikintu kinjirira mu dirishya hari umuyaga.

0:00:35.040,0:00:39.620
Ako kanya, abagera kuri batatu bahise bapfa igihe yasengaga.

0:00:39.620,0:00:43.040
Ndagusabye, ngwino! Yesu aragukunda.

0:00:43.040,0:00:48.420
Nyuma Umuhanuzi T.B.Joshua yatanze ubuhanuzi burambuye bw'ibyo birori bidasanzwe byabaye,

0:00:48.420,0:00:51.640
umugabo yegereye umuhanuzi byihuse.

0:00:51.640,0:00:53.020
Mureke tumwumve.

0:00:53.020,0:00:56.020
Nitwa Ubong Emah Willie.

0:00:56.020,0:01:00.560
Nkomoka muri Leta ya Akwa Ibom (Nigeria)

0:01:00.560,0:01:03.620
Naguze ikibanza hashize imyaka myinshi.

0:01:03.620,0:01:08.680
Nubatse inzu kandi nsakara ibyumba bitatu byayo.

0:01:08.680,0:01:10.960
Hanyuma ntumira umuntu w'Imana ngo aze asengz.

0:01:10.960,0:01:16.040
Ako kanya umuvugabutumwa atangira gusenga, igini ryinjira mu nzu,

0:01:16.040,0:01:21.140
ryica abana banjye babiri. N'uwo muvugabutumwa nawe arapfa.

0:01:21.140,0:01:23.140
Bavuga ko ari nde wabiteye?

0:01:23.140,0:01:25.780
Bavuge ko arinjye ntandaro.

0:01:25.780,0:01:27.460
Kandi barashaka kukwica?

0:01:27.460,0:01:28.500
Yego.

0:01:28.500,0:01:37.760
Ndashaka guhagarara hano nkababwira ko ba nyirabayazana bari ahongaho.

0:01:37.760,0:01:42.340
Ntabwo ikibazo kizakemuka gusa ahubwo bazashyirwa no ku karubanda.

0:01:48.260,0:01:56.340
Bantu ba Akwa Ibom - mushimire Imana ko abantu banyu bazi icyo  Imana ya T.B.Joshua ishobora gukora.

0:01:56.340,0:02:01.160
Kuko babibonye, ntabwo ari umwe, ntabwo ari babiri, ntabwo ari batatu.

0:02:01.160,0:02:06.460
Ndashaka kubabwira yuko uyu mugabo nta kintu azi na kimwe.

0:02:06.460,0:02:10.300
Mana urakoze, Yesu. Ni byo.

0:02:10.300,0:02:15.820
Nta kintu azi na kimwe cyerekeye uru rupfu.

0:02:15.820,0:02:20.860
Umuntu wohereje iryo gini ni umuntu w'umukene.

0:02:20.860,0:02:24.280
Kuva mu ntangiriro, wari ufite ibibazo by'icyo kibanza.

0:02:24.280,0:02:26.960
Yego, Igihe cyose najyaga mu rusengero bambwiraga ko ikibanza atari cyiza.

0:02:26.960,0:02:29.120
Sinari mbizi ariko umuvugabutumwa yasengaga buri gihe.

0:02:29.120,0:02:30.480
Ndashaka kugira icyo nkubwira.

0:02:30.480,0:02:35.840
Umuvugabutumwa waje aho ngaho kugusengera, yakoresheje amaguru ye abiri kugera aho?

0:02:35.840,0:02:36.520
Yego.

0:02:36.520,0:02:37.660
Yaba yararwaye mbere?

0:02:37.660,0:02:38.480
Oya.

0:02:38.480,0:02:39.220
Ha!

0:02:39.220,0:02:41.420
N'abana banjye babiri ntabwo bari barwaye.

0:02:41.420,0:02:42.700
Abana bawe ntabwo bari barwaye?

0:02:42.700,0:02:43.600
Ntabwo bari barwaye.

0:02:43.600,0:02:45.000
Oke, ni byo.

0:02:45.000,0:02:49.060
Aka ni akazi katoroshye.

0:02:49.060,0:02:50.760
Iyo ni Imyuka y'amagini kuri mwe

0:02:50.760,0:02:54.500
Niba udashobora kubabohora , bazakubohora.

0:02:54.500,0:02:58.660
Igihe uwo mugabo atashoboraga kubabohora, bo baramubohoye.

0:02:58.660,0:03:05.860
Uyu mu gabo ntabwo ari umupfumu ntacyo aricyo.

0:03:05.860,0:03:09.280
Ni ikiremwa muntu, nkamwe.

0:03:09.280,0:03:14.720
Nyuma y'uko ibyo biba, hari ahantu bashakako  ujya na none.

0:03:14.720,0:03:17.460
Washakaga kubakurikira ariko nyuma waravuze ngo :"oya"

0:03:17.460,0:03:20.440
Niyo mpamvu bavuze ngo niwowe wabishe .

0:03:20.440,0:03:22.660
Sinzi uko bita aho hantu.

0:03:22.660,0:03:30.020
Baravuze ngo nshobora kujyana nabo ahantu ariko nanze kubakurikira.

0:03:30.020,0:03:35.640
Umuvugabutumwa watumiye, wapfiriye mu nzu yawe, ni iki wamubajije kandi ni iki yagukoreye?

0:03:35.640,0:03:38.560
Namubwiye ko yaza akansengera kuko nashaka kwimukira mu nzu nshya.

0:03:38.560,0:03:41.060
Oke, Wamubwiye kugukurikira no kugusengera?

0:03:41.060,0:03:41.700
Yego.

0:03:41.700,0:03:43.000
Kuko washakaga kwimukira mu nzu yawe?

0:03:43.000,0:03:43.840
Yego.

0:03:43.840,0:03:45.460
Ako kanya batangiye gusenga...

0:03:45.460,0:03:47.680
....igini ririnjira.

0:03:47.680,0:03:52.760
Iryo ni isengesho bwoko ki umuvugabutumwa yasengaga mbere yuko igini ryinjira?

0:03:52.760,0:03:54.300
Umugabutumwa yavugaga yuko icyo kibanza atari cyiza.

0:03:54.300,0:03:58.920
ko hari imyuka mibi kandi ko tugomba gusenga tukayirukana.

0:03:58.920,0:04:01.560
ndi umuhamya. Nkomoka mu rusisiro rwe.

0:04:01.560,0:04:04.020
Izina ryanjye ni Ikpe Friday, nkomoka muri urwo rusisiro

0:04:04.020,0:04:10.120
Twatekerezaga ko akoresha abana be mu mihango y'amafaranga.

0:04:10.120,0:04:11.480
Ok. Abatuye urusisiro bose?

0:04:11.480,0:04:15.040
Abatuye urusisiro bose batekereza yuko akoresha abana be mu mihango y'amafaranga.

0:04:15.040,0:04:16.140
Ntabwo abakoresha muri iyo mihango.

0:04:16.140,0:04:21.720
Urakoze Yesu, Urakoze Mana!

0:04:21.720,0:04:24.840
Mureke tugende.

0:04:24.840,0:04:26.560
Imana ihabwe Icyubahiro!

0:04:26.560,0:04:32.200
Ukuri kwaragaragaye igihe umugabo ukomoka mu murenge wa Ubong yaje kubihamya

0:04:32.200,0:04:35.420
ko ubuhanuzi bwatanzwe bwari ukuri.

0:04:35.420,0:04:39.280
Ndi umuvandimwe w'uyu mugabo. Ntashobora kuvuga neza.

0:04:39.280,0:04:42.520
Igihe ibi bintu byabaye, umuyobozi w'akarere ka Paramount Ruler yohereje

0:04:42.520,0:04:46.060
itsinda ry'abantu bo kwiga iki kibazo.

0:04:46.060,0:04:51.140
ibintu byatugeje muri Leta ya Bayelsa aho twagiye kugisha inama umupfumu,

0:04:51.140,0:04:53.380
n'ubwo atajyanye natwe, jye nagiyeyo.

0:04:53.380,0:04:56.680
Umupfumu yavuze yuko uyu mugabo atabirimo,

0:04:56.680,0:04:58.760
ko ikibazo cyaturutse ku kibanza.

0:04:58.760,0:05:01.580
igihe twagarutse mu rusisiro muri Leta ya Akwa Ibom,

0:05:01.580,0:05:06.160
ntawigeze abyemera, ahubwo bashatse kumubamba. Ariruka.

0:05:06.160,0:05:10.120
Nyuma Umuyobozi mukuru aravuga ngo aho yizera honyine

0:05:10.120,0:05:13.500
hashobora gukemura icyo kibazo kandi bakagira icyo babwira

0:05:13.500,0:05:17.920
buri muntu yashobora kwizera ni kuri SCOAN  kwa T.B.Joshua.

0:05:25.360,0:05:34.400
Ndabashimiye bantu bo muri Akwa Ibom. Mbega icyubahiro n'ubutoni!

0:05:34.400,0:05:38.960
Ndabashimiye na none kandi ndashaka kubabwira yuko bantu ba akwa Ibom,

0:05:38.960,0:05:45.960
igihe nsenga, buri gihe ndabibuka mu isengesho

0:05:45.960,0:05:49.580
kubera icyubahiro n'ubutoni mu mpa.

0:05:49.580,0:05:54.440
Nzi yuko ibintu byinshi byabaye mu gihe cyashize.

0:05:54.440,0:05:56.820
Ariko kugira ngo mwemere Imana,

0:05:56.820,0:06:02.480
ko iyo mvuze ikintu kiba kivuye mu ijuru, murakoze cyane kubera ibyo.

0:06:02.480,0:06:07.960
Mufite umuntu ubasengera.

0:06:07.960,0:06:11.320
Mwagiye ahantu henshi?

0:06:11.320,0:06:15.280
Yego, nibyo. Twagiye ahantu muri Leta ya Bayelsa.

0:06:15.280,0:06:16.820
Bababwiye iki?

0:06:16.820,0:06:19.780
Umupfumu yavuze yuko uyu mugabo ari umwere,

0:06:19.780,0:06:21.500
nubwo uyu ubwe atari yaje.

0:06:21.500,0:06:26.300
Igihe tugarutse, twabwiye Umuyobozi w'umurenge icyo umupfumu yari yatubwiye.

0:06:26.300,0:06:31.200
Nta muntu webyemeye, ahubwo barashaka kwica uyu mugabo.

0:06:31.200,0:06:33.600
Umurambo w'umuvugabutumwa ntabwo wari wahambwa,

0:06:33.600,0:06:36.580
mu gihe abo bana babiri bahambwe.

0:06:36.580,0:06:42.900
Abaturanyi baravuga ngo umuhungu w'uwo muvugabutumwa ashobora kuba umuhamya w'urwo rugendo; yicaye hano.

0:06:42.900,0:06:43.720
Arihe umuhungu we?

0:06:43.720,0:06:45.260
Umuhungu wa w'umuvugabutumwa ari inyuma.

0:06:45.260,0:06:47.140
Ndagusabye genda umuzane.

0:06:47.140,0:06:49.360
Victor!

0:06:49.360,0:06:53.940
Umuhungu w'umuvugabutumwa ari mu rusengero umuhamya w'ibintu byose,

0:06:53.940,0:06:57.060
mbere yuko bica uyu mugabo.

0:06:57.060,0:07:00.280
Victor, ndagusabye ngwino!

0:07:00.280,0:07:03.360
Mureke turebe ekara.

0:07:03.360,0:07:08.920
Wumvise ibisobanuro by'uyu mugabo nk'umugabo wiboneye ibyabaye mu rusisisro.

0:07:08.920,0:07:12.580
Yaravuze ngo igihe iki kibazo cyabaye, buri muntu mu murenge yarabyemeye

0:07:12.580,0:07:15.900
ko uyu mugabo ari ntandaro y'urupfu rw'umuvugabutumwa

0:07:15.900,0:07:18.500
kandi ko akoresha abana be mu mihango.

0:07:18.500,0:07:22.300
kandi bagiye ahantu henshi mu iperereza ry'icyabiteye

0:07:22.300,0:07:24.220
bababwira yuko uyu mugabo ari umwere

0:07:24.220,0:07:26.780
ariko ntawe ubyemera mu rusisiro rwose

0:07:26.780,0:07:31.300
kandi uko ni ko bose bifatanyije mu rusisiro...

0:07:31.300,0:07:35.060
Uyu ni umuhungu wa nyakwigendera Umuvugabutumwa naho uyu mugabo ahagarariye umuyobozi w'akarere.

0:07:35.060,0:07:37.760
Ni umugabo umuyobozi mukuru yabwiye kuzana natwe,

0:07:37.760,0:07:41.660
mu gihe jywe mpagarariye abatuye aho ibyo byabereye.

0:07:41.660,0:07:43.360
Waba uri umuhungu w'umuvugabutumwa?

0:07:43.360,0:07:44.880
Yego.

0:07:44.880,0:07:46.240
Sawa.

0:07:46.240,0:07:49.980
Twumvise ibyabaye kuri so. Ushobora kutubwira ibyabaye ?

0:07:49.980,0:07:53.680
Amanuweli (Imana Iri kumwe natwe - Matayo 1:23)

0:07:53.680,0:07:58.320
Izina ryanjye ni Victor Anthony.

0:07:58.320,0:08:02.400
Ndashimira Imana cyane; Imana yahinduye ubuzima bwanjye.

0:08:02.400,0:08:05.280
Mbere nakoraga ibintu bimeze nk'ibyumusazi.

0:08:05.280,0:08:08.740
Iyo nabaga mfite ikibazo, nashoboraga kwirukanka.

0:08:08.740,0:08:14.860
Igihe numvise ko Data yapfuye, narahungabanye-

0:08:14.860,0:08:17.220
Nahungabanyijwe  n'uyu

0:08:17.220,0:08:20.280
Igihe mbajije Mama, arambwira ngo uyu ni umuntu

0:08:20.280,0:08:23.460
waje gutumira so muri iyi nzu.

0:08:23.460,0:08:27.020
aramubajije ngo :"Ni gute waje gutumira Data iwawe? gukora iki?"

0:08:27.020,0:08:31.900
Aravuga ngo : "uyu mugabo ajya gushaka abahanuzi ahantu hatandukanye

0:08:31.900,0:08:37.240
nuko ajyana  Data kumusengera mu nzu ye" kugira ngo asengere inzu ye .

0:08:37.240,0:08:41.140
Naramubajine nti :"Ni iki uwo mugabo yashyize mu nzu ye kugira ngo atumire Data amusenge?

0:08:41.140,0:08:44.700
Imana ntabwo yahaye Data impano yo gusenga ariko impano yo kuba umubwirizabutumwa.

0:08:44.700,0:08:46.360
Data yari umuvugabutumwa.

0:08:46.360,0:08:48.940
Sinavuze yuko ari akazi katoroshye.

0:08:48.940,0:08:50.500
Murabizi yuko nabivuze?

0:08:50.500,0:08:53.940
Sinigeze mwumvana na rimwe ko se yari umunyamasengesho.

0:08:53.940,0:08:57.120
Umuhungu we aravuga ko atigeze amenya ko se yari umunyamasengesho.

0:08:57.120,0:09:02.120
Kuki bagombaga guhamagara uwo mugabo ngo aze asenge?

0:09:02.120,0:09:05.160
Yaravuze ngo uyu mugabo yapfushije abana babiri.

0:09:05.160,0:09:08.180
Igihe mbyumvise narakangaranye.

0:09:08.180,0:09:10.660
Bambwiye ko Data ari mu bitaro.

0:09:10.660,0:09:14.060
Nirukiye mu bitaro kureba Data, Data yari yapfuye.

0:09:14.060,0:09:15.940
Najyanye Data mu rusengero.

0:09:15.940,0:09:18.820
Data baramusengera ariko ntacyo byatanze.

0:09:18.820,0:09:20.820
abantu bamwe bavuye ahandi hantu.

0:09:20.820,0:09:25.720
Mbere y'aho, nari fipte akamenyero ko kurakara.

0:09:25.720,0:09:30.820
Abantu bambwiye ngo dushobora kugenda tugatwika inzu y'uwo mugabo tukaba imbarutso mu mugi wowse.

0:09:30.820,0:09:36.920
Naravuze ngo :"oya, mureke dukurikire amahoro mbere y'ibintu byose"

0:09:36.920,0:09:40.900
Kuko ntari uko nari meze mbere, twagerageje kubikemura mu mahoro.

0:09:40.900,0:09:44.480
Nahuye nuyu mugabo hanyuma twumvikana ko aza akambika Data.

0:09:44.480,0:09:47.900
Nakoze urutonde rw'ibyo agomba gukoresha mu guhamba Data.

0:09:47.900,0:09:52.120
Urutonde rw'ibyo nakoze rugera kuri miliyoni 4 za naira.

0:09:56.800,0:10:03.620
Dushobora guceceka tukumva Ugushaka kw'Imana ku byerekeye iki kibazo?

0:10:03.620,0:10:08.680
Nabivuze kuko nari nabajije abankuriye.

0:10:08.680,0:10:11.440
ikintu nk'iki cyari cyarabaye mbere. Baravuze ngo ,"oya".

0:10:11.440,0:10:13.440
Kuva navuka, sinigeze mbona ibintu nk'ibi.

0:10:13.440,0:10:19.220
Umuntu w'Imana ajya gusengera abantu nuko ububasha bw'igini mu nzu bukica abantu.

0:10:19.220,0:10:23.240
Nimubona abo bantu muzababwire ko bishwe n'imyuka mibi,

0:10:23.240,0:10:26.340
ntimuzabyemera, muzatekereza yuko bakubiswe n'umuntu uri mu mubiri nkanjye.

0:10:26.340,0:10:30.220
Kuko byari bimeze nk'aho bakoresheje icyuma gishyushye babakubita.

0:10:30.220,0:10:32.220
Igihe icyo gisate cy'icyuma gikoreshejwe ku muntu, uruhu rwe rurashishuka.

0:10:32.220,0:10:35.560
Abana be  babiri bakubiswe n'uwo mwuka mubi

0:10:35.560,0:10:38.580
bakubiswe mu mutwe nuko ubwonko buratandukana.

0:10:38.580,0:10:43.240
Iyo ubabonye ntabwo wavuga ngo ni umwuka mubi wabikoze.

0:10:43.240,0:10:46.800
Muzavuga yuko ari umwicanyi w'umumucancuro wabikoze.

0:10:46.800,0:10:48.880
Ibi bintu byabaye mu buryo ntumva.

0:10:48.880,0:10:51.440
Niyo mpamvu mbwira uyu mugabo ngo aze ahambe Data.

0:10:51.440,0:10:56.080
N'aha hantu naje, abantu bavuze yuko nagombaga kuzana nawe.

0:10:56.080,0:10:58.780
ko nshobora gutegereza kugeza igihe azakemurira ikibazo

0:10:58.780,0:11:06.040
mbere yuko azagaruka kandi agahamba Data kandi akita ku mugore we n'abana be.

0:11:06.040,0:11:10.100
Iki ni ikibazo gikomeye.

0:11:10.100,0:11:13.920
Mushobora kubona amananiza akurikiraho.

0:11:13.920,0:11:18.860
Ndabasabye, mure dukemure iki kibazo.

0:11:18.860,0:11:25.080
Ikintu kimwe mugomba kmenya, igihe amagini akora,

0:11:25.080,0:11:29.880
ntuzayabona keretse abari mu mwuka nibo bayabona.

0:11:29.880,0:11:33.120
Baza bameze nk'abantu, bakoresha na bo imbunda.

0:11:33.120,0:11:36.180
Bashobora gukoresha imbunda bica.

0:11:36.180,0:11:41.000
Mu gihe umuntu apfuye, muzabona aho imbunda yarashe mu mubiri.

0:11:41.000,0:11:44.120
Bashobora gukoresha icyuma ariko ntimuzabona umuntu.

0:11:44.120,0:11:50.640
Ariko mu gihe umurambo urambaraye hasi, muzabona ko ari icyuma bakoresheje.

0:11:50.640,0:11:55.500
Rimwe na rimwe, ntacyo bazakoresha nuko umuntu agapfa atyo.

0:11:55.500,0:12:03.760
Ntabwo muzabona na hamwe yakubiswe, yatemwe yatewe icyumwa ...

0:12:03.760,0:12:10.700
Muvandimwe, ndashaka kukubwira yuko uyu muvandimwa atari umupfumu.

0:12:10.700,0:12:17.920
Hari amagini amwe  akoreshwa kuri ubwo buryo kugira ngo akocore.

0:12:17.920,0:12:22.900
Ubu, ku birebana no kwita ku muryango wawe n'ibindi byose,

0:12:22.900,0:12:25.040
Sinshaka yuko mushyiraho amananiza.

0:12:25.040,0:12:28.300
Ndashaka guhura nawe kugira ngo tubirangize.

0:12:28.300,0:12:32.780
Ariko icy'ingenzi nuko uyu mugabo atariwe wishe so.

0:12:32.780,0:12:35.140
Ntabwo ari igini, ntabwo ari umupfumu.

0:12:35.140,0:12:40.380
Ndashimira abantu bo muri Akwa Ibom kuba bazanye iki kibazo hano uyu munsi.

0:12:40.380,0:12:42.180
Ndabishimiye cyane.

0:12:42.180,0:12:50.060
Nimva hano uyu munsi ndajya gusengera Leta ya Akwa Ibom.

0:12:50.060,0:12:52.820
Uyu mugabo ntabwo ari umupfumu.

