Ndashaka kubohora uyu mugabo mu  bibazo yarimo, kuva atariwe wishe so.

0:13:38.740,0:13:45.040
kugira ngo muhe guhumeka bityo ave mu bya muziritse,

0:13:45.040,0:13:50.000
