0:14:22.640,0:14:28.520
Ndagusabye, ku bwanjye, ndashaka kubona umubyeyi wawe, umuryango wawe n'abana.

0:14:28.520,0:14:31.120
Ku bwanjye iyo ni inkunga yanjye.

0:14:31.120,0:14:38.560
Nzaha umuryango N500.000 kugira ngo utangire kandi bibagirwe icyo kibazo.

0:14:38.560,0:14:44.860
Muvandimwe, reba umurimo wo so yagiye gukora nk'umurimo w'Imana.

0:14:44.860,0:14:47.780
Urupfu yapfuye si ikibazo.

