0:15:13.160,0:15:15.780
Ugukiranuka kw'Imana ni ko gufite akamaro.

0:15:15.780,0:15:17.480
Ndashaka ko mwubaha so.

0:15:17.480,0:15:23.880
Yagiye mu butumwa bwo gusenga kandi kugira ngo so agume mu mahoro,

0:15:23.880,0:15:27.300
